data.description: Expansive 4-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home located in the sought after Preserves at Southlake.  Upon entry you will notice the large, well-lit office/formal dining room.  The eat-in, open-concept kitchen is spacious with a large island, granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances.  This home offers a main floor in-law suite, with a large, 2nd level, primary bedroom.  The primary bedroom features dual walk-in closets and an en-suite bathroom.  Chill out, relax or party in the other 3 bedrooms and spacious gathering area on the 2nd floor. The house backs up to a wooded area, featuring a screened in porch great for cookouts and gatherings. Seller is offering a 5k buyers credit for the right offer!  Don't miss your chance, see it TODAY!!
